{{Infobox person | name = Carolus Nolet | image = | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{birth based on age as of date |76|2017|02|06|}}<ref name="Forbes" /> | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | restingplace = | nationality = Dutch | religion = | ethnicity = | residence = [[Schiedam]], Netherlands | education = | alma mater = | occupation = | title = Chairman, [[Ketel One]] | term = 1979 | predecessor = | successor = | known for = | boards = | salary = | networth = US$2.4 billion (February 2017)<ref name="Forbes" /> | spouse = married | parents = | children = 2 | relations = | website = }}
'''Carolus Nolet''' (born 1940/41) is a Dutch [[billionaire]], and the chairman of the Netherlands-based [[Ketel One]] drinks company.<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web|title=The World's Billionaires: Carolus Nolet|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/carolus-nolet-sr/|website=Forbes|accessdate=8 February 2017}}</ref>
Nolet is married with two children and lives in [[Schiedam]], Netherlands.<ref name="Forbes" />
